Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: PGA Financial Plaza is a premier four-story Class-A office building in a prominent location at the corner of PGA Blvd. and Fairchild Gardens Ave., just one mile east of I-95. This prime location offers easy access to arterial roads and is within walking distance to numerous dining, shopping and banking options. It's close to all of Palm Beach Garden's conveniences including The Gardens Mall, Downtown at the Gardens and Legacy Place.  This meticulously maintained building features first-class finishes throughout with on-site management and maintenance. It's also the highest Energy Star rated building on PGA and has received a 90+ Energy Star score for the last 6+ years.  Advanced Trane Tracer energy management system provides personalized HVAC comfort.
